      <br>• Low hours (typically 3,000-6,000 hours)
      <br>• Like-new condition at 70-80% of new price
      <br>• Long remaining useful life (8,000+ hours)</p>

      <p><strong>Best For:</strong>
      <br>• Contractors wanting near-new at lower cost
      <br>• Long-term projects (5+ years)
